Hey, wait up!

112
00:03:32,504 --> 00:03:33,714
Whoop, whoop!

113
00:03:34,131 --> 00:03:36,174
Whoop, whoop, whoop!

114
00:03:36,258 --> 00:03:38,552
Whoop, whoop, whoop!

115
00:03:38,635 --> 00:03:39,970
Whoop!
Whoop!

116
