in the cliff side.

126
00:04:10,125 --> 00:04:11,460
Amazing!

127
00:04:11,543 --> 00:04:13,837
Yeah, I poked around in there
a bit, but --

128
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:15,964
Dut, dut, dut!
No spoilers!

129
00:04:16,047 --> 00:04:17,382
No, I know.

130
00:04:17,466 --> 00:04:18,842
I didn't go past
