134
00:04:27,100 --> 00:04:29,895
Hey ya, hey ya, hey ya!

135
00:04:30,103 --> 00:04:31,438
Come on.

136
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:36,610
This way.

137
00:04:37,861 --> 00:04:39,321
