What the?!

160
00:05:37,921 --> 00:05:38,922
Fern?

161
00:05:42,259 --> 00:05:43,426
Fern?

162
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:45,929
[ Grunting ]

163
00:05:47,597 --> 00:05:49,140
Uh, Fern?

164
00:05:49,224 --> 00:05:51,560
