with a new bucket of trash.

181
00:06:36,479 --> 00:06:37,480
Later!

182
00:06:40,483 --> 00:06:41,693
Fern!?

183
00:06:41,776 --> 00:06:43,528
[ Grunts ]

184
00:06:43,612 --> 00:06:45,739
I've been double-crossed
by grass Finn!

185
00:06:49,284 --> 00:06:51,578
I don't like being abandoned!

186
00:06:51,661 --> 00:06:53,455
I'm sensitive to it!

187
00:06:53,997 --> 00:06:55,415
[ Groans ]

188
00:06:55,498 --> 00:06:56,583
Mmm!

189
00:06:58,752 --> 00:07:00,503
[ Sighs ]
It's too hot!

190
00:07:03,173 --> 00:07:04,215
[ Groans ]

191
00:07:04,299 --> 00:07:05,634
[ Muttering ]

192
00:07:05,717 --> 00:07:08,011
There's got to be
something useful in here.

193
00:07:14,476 --> 00:07:15,894
[ Screams ]

194
00:07:15,977 --> 00:07:17,312
Oof!

195
00:07:19,189 --> 00:07:20,607
You'll be back in a month?

196
00:07:20,690 --> 00:07:22,442
With a new bucket of trash?

197
00:07:23,068 --> 00:07:25,111
It's hot!
There's no air in here!

198
00:07:25,195 --> 00:07:26,947
I need air!

199
00:07:27,030 --> 00:07:28,198
I need air!

200
00:07:29,199 --> 00:07:32,619
[ Whirring ]

201
00:07:32,702 --> 00:07:35,956
Wha?

202
00:07:36,539 --> 00:07:37,457
Oh!

203
00:07:37,958 --> 00:07:39,209
A microphone.

204
00:07:39,417 --> 00:07:40,877
