218
00:08:11,908 --> 00:08:13,660
Okay, um...

219
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:16,454
Welcome, Finn!

220
00:08:17,580 --> 00:08:18,957
Huh.

221
00:08:26,881 --> 00:08:28,299
Yes!

222
00:08:37,142 --> 00:08:38,977
[ Buzzing ]

223
00:08:39,060 --> 00:08:39,978
Huh?

224
00:08:40,061 --> 00:08:41,187
