235
00:09:04,044 --> 00:09:05,920
You've been Finn
long enough!

236
00:09:06,004 --> 00:09:07,672
It's my turn.

237
00:09:07,756 --> 00:09:09,090
[ Growls ]

238
00:09:09,174 --> 00:09:11,301
Fern, smarten up!

239
00:09:11,885 --> 00:09:13,428
Nuh-uh!

240
00:09:14,179 --> 00:09:15,472
