241
00:09:15,555 --> 00:09:17,348
A weed whacker!

242
00:09:17,557 --> 00:09:19,142
[ Hissing ]

243
00:09:22,228 --> 00:09:24,314
[ Grunting ]

244
00:09:24,397 --> 00:09:26,608
Nyuh!

245
00:09:29,861 --> 00:09:31,488
[ Hisses ]

246
00:09:35,909 --> 00:09:37,535
My belzer!

247
00:09:37,619 --> 00:09:38,995
[ Grunting ]

248
00:09:39,662 --> 00:09:40,830
Whoa!

249
00:09:42,540 --> 00:09:44,417
[ Panting ]

250
00:09:47,378 --> 00:09:48,797
[ Laughs ]

251
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:51,216
Fern, if things
are going down the way

252
00:09:51,299 --> 00:09:52,842
I think they're going down --

253
00:09:52,926 --> 00:09:55,220
please tell Jake
I love him.

254
00:09:55,303 --> 00:09:56,513
That doesn't matter.

255
00:09:56,596 --> 00:09:57,514
I love him!

256
00:09:58,014 --> 00:09:59,390
